                    <comment id="12521562" author="reschke" created="Tue, 21 Aug 2007 20:45:00 +0100"  >Hm.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
I&amp;#39;m not really sure why we have a dependency on Xerces at all. The JDKs ship with their own version of Xerces, and I think we should use those.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
</comment>
                    <comment id="12521564" author="jukkaz" created="Tue, 21 Aug 2007 20:52:57 +0100"  >&amp;gt; I&amp;#39;m not really sure why we have a dependency on Xerces at all.&lt;br/&gt;
